286
00:15:45,943 --> 00:15:46,364
Come si chiama?

287
00:15:47,323 --> 00:15:48,644
Michela Idiong.

288
00:15:49,446 --> 00:15:53,128
Figlia di immigrati dalla Nigeria.

289
00:15:53,148 --> 00:15:53,908
Molto affascinante.

290
